title: MOOSE SCARY DAIRY SHORT
description: http://www.neffheadwear.com/skate Recently turned pro, Luis de los Reyes, aka Moose shreds an old "haunted" dairy farm in Camarillo, California otherwise know as Scary Dairy. Watch Moose tag up and rip up Scary Dairy decked out in Neff gear. In this 1:25 clip, you will find his steezy skateboarding style matches his cool demeanor.
